title: Intern Haenyeo
description: It’s the generation of the Corona outbreak! Due to a shortage of medical personnel, “Hwang Gwangho,” an intern doctor, was forcibly assigned to a place called “Mermaid Village.” One day, he meets “Hyeyeon,” one of the village’s haenyeos who is defenselessly undressing by the beach and his seemingly ordinary life begins to overflow with their sexual relationship. “Were haenyeos supposed to look this sexy in their suits…?”
author: Chungnyang
